  15 Jan 2012; Ole Markus With <olemarkus@gentoo.org> libvirt-php-0.4.1.ebuild,
  libvirt-php-9999.ebuild:
  Remove PHP_USE.

  13 Jul 2011; Tiziano Müller <dev-zero@gentoo.org> libvirt-php-9999.ebuild:
  Migrated to new git-2.eclass.

